    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. You can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road without any immediate repair needs.",
