    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock for superior traction. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis's structural integrity. The exterior retains its factory-original paint depth, while the interior's Nappa leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning collector who demands peak performance and technical purity.",
